{"tid":639008,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"我係鋤Dee既A，投降輸一半得唔得？","createTime":"2018-04-23T07:28:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-23T11:30:07.000Z","uid":66004,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"2071e80ce094d7d4637b86fd4c267a847be9b5dd","tid":639008,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:28:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/23/100538_726bef3ff05e2325506c6739ffb05c87.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F23%2F100538_726bef3ff05e2325506c6739ffb05c87.png&h=36c57077&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已知策略：<br />\n1) A出3<br />\n2) B pass<br />\n<br />\n原因：<br />\n1) B有最大的pair(pair Dee)，所以A一開始只能出單支，故出3<br />\n2) 如果B不pass，反而出6/Dee：<br />\n----2.1) B出Dee -&gt; A出心Dee -&gt; <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">A得到主動權並只有一張單支(Ace)，而B沒有了pair Dee</span></strong> -&gt; A便可以屈pair -&gt; 最後A只剩一張單支(Ace) -&gt; A贏.<br />\n----2.2) B出6 -&gt; A出Ace -&gt; <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">B只可以pass，因為如果拆了pair Dee出Dee後，A仍可以出心Dee獲取主動權並且手上沒有任何單支，而B只剩一張單支(Dee)</span></strong> -&gt;  A便可以屈pair -&gt; A贏.<br />\n<br />\n現在：<br />\nA手牌: 4455QQKKA2 (有主動權並有2張單支)<br />\nB手牌: 622<br />\n<br />\n關鍵：<br />\n由於B有最大的pair，A只可以繼續出單支，問題是1)拆pair 4出4 2)拆pair Q出Q 3)出Ace 有可能贏呢？<br />\n<br />\n1) A拆pair 4出4 -&gt; B出2 -&gt; A出心Dee -&gt; A既[4、Ace、pairs] vs B既[6、Dee] -&gt; B贏.<br />\n<br />\n2) A拆pair Q出Q -&gt; B出2 -&gt; A出心Dee -&gt; A既[Q、Ace、pairs] vs B既[6、Dee] -&gt; B贏.<br />\n<br />\n3) A出Ace -&gt; B不可以拆pair Dee出Dee，因為A可以出心Dee，然後屈pair -&gt; 因此B pass -&gt; A只可以一直拆牌，因為B仍有pair Dee -&gt; 直到A出4/5 -&gt; B出6 -&gt; A不論出心Dee或Q/K -&gt; 到最後都會有2張比Dee細的單支 -&gt; A既[Low1、Low2、pairs] vs B既[2、2] -&gt; B贏.<br />\n<br />\n結論： B sure wins, <span style=\"color: red;\">如果B識出的話</span>。<br />\n<br />\n重點：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">B要Keep pair Dee，以防對方只剩下1張單支(/1張單支 + 1張心Dee)然後屈pair</span><br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">B如果決定打單支Dee，要確保A有2張細於Dee的單支</span>"},{"pid":"fabfba7fcd0097da6437395038aa30b490bca870","tid":639008,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:48:44.000Z","msg":"覺得係A既可以跟住上面玩一次，然後搵錯處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e187b0779ccf85e64a7f8101182dc933418cc275","tid":639008,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"只要B pass到對面嘅pair Q,K出晒就會贏，B冇得輸"},{"pid":"c920924df6273ffc5059a1e8d4f997166e3c5833","tid":639008,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e187b0779ccf85e64a7f8101182dc933418cc275","tid":639008,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:50:59.000Z","msg":"只要B pass到對面嘅pair Q,K出晒就會贏，B冇得輸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T07:56:49.000Z","msg":"係 你咁樣講仲易明 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5237b792db53836e36f3d17881ec3a0e353975de","tid":639008,"uid":14840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"如果A行單支，咁會點？"},{"pid":"c80638721cad2e4ed63058b14571c459ba51f14e","tid":639008,"uid":100230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5237b792db53836e36f3d17881ec3a0e353975de","tid":639008,"uid":14840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"如果A行單支，咁會點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:28:50.000Z","msg":"b出一隻2引 a隻2出"},{"pid":"a337118953c22a269170f25e1c1f2d733929b1c9","tid":639008,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5237b792db53836e36f3d17881ec3a0e353975de","tid":639008,"uid":14840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T08:21:29.000Z","msg":"如果A行單支，咁會點？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T09:07:28.000Z","msg":"唔明<br />\n<br />\nA係B拆pair Dee之前都要行單支"},{"pid":"94da714e0111d6992bd3567a732181b521b4c09b","tid":639008,"uid":66004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-23T11:07:03.000Z","msg":"facebook都